text: Hernán Oelckers (25 December 1925 - 2009) was a Chilean alpine skier. He competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Chilean male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Chile Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Santiago
